# Meriter Architecture

**Target blueprint:** `.index/architecture/TARGET_ARCHITECTURE.md` (Round 36) ¬∑ metadata: `target_architecture.yaml` (schema_version 2) ¬∑ intrinsic complexity: `NECESSARY_COMPLEXITY.md` (30 concepts, **19** bounded contexts). Rules below encode **live repo** layout plus **migration target**; aspirational paths are marked. **Phase 0 not landed** ‚Äî ESLint boundary zones 1‚Äì9 are spec-only until kickoff PR.

## Clean Architecture layers (backend)

| Layer | Live path | Target path | Responsibility |
|-------|-----------|-------------|----------------|
| **Domain** | `domain/` (+ `@InjectModel` in services) | same + **`domain/ports/`** (Phase 3) | Business rules: vote factors, `PermissionRuleEngine`, wallet/quota guards |
| **Application** | logic in `trpc/routers/*`, `createVoteLogic` | **`application/use-cases/`** (Phase 2‚Äì3) | Orchestration, transaction boundaries; **no** `@nestjs/mongoose` |
| **Adapters** | `trpc/`, `api-v1/` | **`adapters/trpc|rest|mappers|presenters|enrichment|resolvers/`** (Phase 2) | Thin transport: validate ‚Üí use case ‚Üí map ‚Üí attach `ResourcePermissions` |
| **Infrastructure** | `domain/models/*`, `api-v1/auth/*`, `tg-bots/`, cron in `domain/services/*-cron*` | **`infrastructure/persistence|auth|storage|telegram|cron|permissions/`** (Phase 2+) | Frameworks, IO, cron; **implements domain ports** |
| **Composition root** | `meriter.module.ts`, `domain.module.ts`, `main.ts` | same | Nest DI only |
| **Cross-cutting** | `common/filters`, `common/interceptors`, `common/schemas` | same (edge) | HTTP envelopes, Sentry, pagination Zod ‚Äî not domain |

**Monorepo rings (dependency direction inward):** `web` ‚Üí `libs/shared-types` + tRPC type bridge; `adapters` ‚Üí `application` ‚Üí `domain` + `ports`; `infrastructure` implements `ports`; no `web` ‚Üí `api/apps/meriter/src/**` runtime imports.

### Web layers

| Layer | Path | Role |
|-------|------|------|
| Routes | `app/meriter/**`, `app/a/[token]/` | Thin `*Client.tsx` shells; no business invariants |
| Features | `features/*/` (partial; notifications/favorites **aspirational** Phase 5‚Äì7) | Domain-scoped UI, hooks; consume tRPC + shared-types |
| Design system | `components/atoms|molecules|ui/` | Obsidian Nocturne; ¬´–ó–∞—Å–ª—É–≥–∏¬ª copy |
| Organisms | `components/organisms/` | Shared chrome; **interim** notification list (Phase 7 ‚Üí `features/notifications/`) |
| Client infra | `lib/trpc/`, `lib/api/`, `contexts/AuthContext.tsx` | Session, query invalidation, routing |

## Dependency rules

### Allowed

| From | To | Notes |
|------|-----|-------|
| `web` | `libs/shared-types`, tRPC `AppRouter` type bridge | No backend runtime in frontend |
| `application/use-cases` | `domain/services`, `domain/ports`, `domain/aggregates` | No `@InjectModel`, no `@nestjs/mongoose` |
| `adapters/trpc|rest` | `application`, `adapters/mappers|presenters` | Thin controllers |
| `infrastructure/*` | implements `domain/ports` | Mongoose, S3, OAuth, cron, **permission-gates adapter** |
| `infrastructure/permissions/permission-gates.adapter.ts` | `api-v1/.../permissions-helper.service.ts` | **Sole** allowed infra‚Üíapi-v1 import (zone 7 / V-11) |
| `domain/*` | `libs/shared-types` allowlist only | `value-objects/**`, `taxonomy.ts`, `value-rubricator.ts`, `decree809-tag-remap.ts`; interim monolithic `schemas.ts` (ResourcePermissionsSchema only via **P0-3** named-export rule) until Phase 1 subpath split ‚Äî **not** `@meriter/shared-types/schemas` (subpath absent from `package.json` exports until Phase 1) |
| `PermissionRuleEngine` | `PermissionGatesPort` | **Never** import `permissions-helper` directly |

### Forbidden

- `domain/services` ‚Üí `trpc/*`, `api-v1/*`, `adapters/*`
- `domain/services` ‚Üí `application/use-cases`
- `application/use-cases` ‚Üí `trpc/*`, `api-v1/*`, `@nestjs/mongoose`
- `infrastructure/**` (except adapter) ‚Üí `api-v1/**`
- `features/A` ‚Üí `features/B` internals (public `index.ts` only)

